hc holdings inc hchcn company profile  reuterscom x edition united states africa américa latina عربي argentina brasil canada  deutschland españa france india italia  méxico россия united kingdom united states profile hc holdings inc hchcn related topics stocksstock screenerindustrialsindustrial conglomerates overview news key developments people charts financials analysts research pulse hchcn on new york stock exchange usd  aug  change  chg   prev close  open  days high  days low  volume  avg vol  wk high  wk low  full description hc holdings inc incorporated on february   is a holding company the company operates through seven segments manufacturing marine services insurance telecommunications utilities life sciences and other the companys subsidiaries include schuff international inc schuff which is a structural steel fabricator and erector in the united states global marine systems limited gmsl a provider of engineering and underwater services on submarine cables continental insurance inc a platform for its runoff longterm care business through its two insurance companies united teacher associates insurance company uta and continental general insurance company cgi ptgiinternational carrier services ptgiics a provider of internetbased protocol and timedivision multiplexing tdm access and transport of long distance voice minutes american natural gas ang a compressed natural gas fueling company and pansend life sciences ltd pansend which is focused on supporting healthcare and biotechnology product development its geographical segments are the united states and the united kingdommanufacturing segment schuff international incschuff is a fabricator and erector of structural steel and heavy steel plate schuff fabricates and erects structural steel for commercial and industrial construction projects such as high and lowrise buildings and office complexes hotels and casinos convention centers sports arenas shopping malls hospitals dams bridges mines and power plants schuff also fabricates trusses and girders and is engaged in the fabrication and erection of largediameter water pipes water storage tanks pollution control scrubbers tunnel liners pressure vessels strainers filters separators and a range of customized products schuff consists of three business units spread across steel markets schuff steel company schuff steel engaged in steel fabrication and erection schuff steel management company engaged in the management of smaller projects leveraging subcontractors and the aitken product line aitken which is engaged in the manufacturing of equipment for the oil and gas industry schuff also provides fabricated steel to canada and other countries including panama where schuff owns schuff hopsa engineering inc an engineering design steel fabrication and erection companyschuff steel offers a range of services including designassistdesignbuild preconstruction design and budgeting steel management fabrication erection and building information modeling bim schuff steel management company provides steel fabrication and erection services aitken supplies various products including strainers such as temporary cone and basket strainers tee type strainers vertical and horizontal permanent line strainers fabricated duplex strainers measurement equipment such as orifice meter tubes orifice plates orifice flanges seal pots flow nozzles venturi tubes low loss tubes and straightening vanes and other products such as spectacle blinds paddle blinds drip rings bleed rings and test inserts launchers and pipe spools schuff offers its steel construction services primarily to general contractors and engineering firms that provide a range of projects including hotels and casinos office complexes hospitals manufacturing plants shopping malls and centers sports stadiums power plants restaurants convention facilities entertainment complexes airports schools churches and warehousesmarine services segment global marine systems limitedgmsl is an offshore engineering company focused on specialist subsea services across the market sectors such as telecommunications oil and gas and offshore power gmsls sectors of focus for providing subsea cable services are telecommunications installation and maintenance oil and gas installation and offshore power installation gmsl provides maintenance and installation to its telecommunications customers gmsl provides vessels on standby to repair fiber optic telecommunications cables additionally gmsl provides installation of cable systems including route planning mapping route engineering cablelaying trenching and burial gmsl provides installation maintenance and repair of fiber optic communication and power infrastructure to offshore platforms its primary activities include providing power from shore enabling fiberbased communication between platforms and shorebased systems and installing permanent reservoir monitoring systems which allow customers to monitor subsea seismic data gmsl operates cable laying fleets consisting of approximately seven vessels including over five owned and the other operated through longterm leasesinsurance segment continental insurance incthe insurance segment cig provides longterm care life and annuity coverage to approximately  individuals through its insurance companies the benefits provided by cigs insurance operations help protect policy and certificate holders from the financial hardships associated with illness injury loss of life or income discontinuation cigs life insurance products include traditional term universal and interest sensitive life insurance its annuity products include flexible and single premium deferred annuities cigs life insurance business provides a personal financial safety net for individuals and their families these products provide protection against financial hardship after the death of an insured some of these products also offer a savings element that can help accumulate funds to meet future financial needstelecommunications segment ptgiinternational carrier servicesthe ptgiics business unit provides customers with internetbased protocol and tdm access and transport of long distance voice minutes ptgiics operates a global telecommunications network consisting of international gateway and domestic switching and related peripheral equipment carriergrade routers and switches for internet and circuitbased services ptgiics network employs digital switching and fiber optic technologies incorporates the use of voice over internet protocol voip protocols and signaling system c ssc signaling ptgiics network makes use of a carriergrade international gateway and domestic switch system internet routers and media gateways in the united states with points of presence through thirdparty interconnections ptgiics owns and operates network management systems in herndon virginia which are used to monitor and control its switching systems global data network and other digital transmission equipment used in its network additional network monitoring network management and traffic management services are supported from the companys contingent network management center located in guatemala city guatemala ptgiics markets its services through a range of sales channels such as trade shows and business developmentutilities segment american natural gasamerican natural gas ang is a compressed natural gas cng fueling company that designs builds owns operates and maintains natural gas fueling stations for the transportation industry angs principal business is supplying cng for light medium and heavyduty vehicles and providing operation repair and maintenance services for vehicle fleet customer stations ang sells cng through fueling stations cng fueling station sales are made through stations located either on ang owned or on angs customers properties and through angs network of public access fueling stations ang performs operate and maintain o and m services for cng stations that are owned by their customerslife sciences segment pansend life sciences ltdthe life sciences segment focuses on the development of technologies and products in healthcare pansend is focused on supporting healthcare and biotechnology product development » full overview of hchcn company address hc holdings inc  park ave fl new york   ny    p f  company web links home page officers  directors name compensation philip falcone  michael sena  suzi herbst  andrea mancuso  paul robinson  » more officers  directors hc holdings inc news briefphilip mittleman reports  pct passive stake in hc holdings as of july   sec filing jul   briefhc holding reduces stake in blue vision jun   » more hchcn news related topics stocksstock screenerindustrialsindustrial conglomerates asiaussubscribesubscribelog insee all companiessearchhc holdings inchchcus nyseadd to watchlistcompany  peoplequotecompany  peoplefinancialsresearch  ratingsadvanced chartmarket open  aug    am et real time quotevolumekopen priceday range   wk range  ytd changefeedback on our new quotesemail uscompany descriptionhc holdings inc engages in the acquisition and grow attractive businesses that generate sustainable free cash flow it operates through following business segments manufacturing marine services insurance telecommunications utilities life sciences and other the manufacturing segment is a structural steel fabricator and erector in the united states the marine services segment provides engineering and underwater services on submarine cables the insurance segment is a platform for there runoff longterm care business through its two insurance companies united teacher associates insurance company and continental general insurance company the telecommunications segment is a provider of internetbased protocol and timedivision multiplexing access and transport of long distance voice minutes the utilities segment is a compressed natural gas fueling company the life sciences segment focuses on supporting healthcare and biotechnology product development the 